<h3 id="joke-names-for-technical-analysis">Joke names for technical analysis</h3>

<p>Crypto traders have invented several joke names for technical analysis, trying to make the point that technical patterns are a fallacy and that lines on chart are completely arbitrary.</p>

<p>There is a larger debate on whether <a href="/technical-analysis/">technical analysis in crypto can actually work</a>, which is not a bad question.</p>

<p>Some of the most common joke names for technical analysis are <strong>t1ts and a$$ (TA)</strong>, <strong>astrology</strong> or <strong>tea leaves</strong>.</p>

